<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Field report — Founding Growth & Customer Associate, Aurox</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Cline x1='50' y1='50' x2='72.6' y2='27.4' stroke='%234A5A63' stroke-width='5' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3Cline x1='50' y1='50' x2='27.4' y2='27.4' stroke='%234A5A63' stroke-width='5' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3Cline x1='50' y1='50' x2='72.6' y2='72.6' stroke='%234A5A63' stroke-width='5' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3Cline x1='50' y1='50' x2='27.4' y2='72.6' stroke='%234A5A63' stroke-width='5' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='72.6' cy='27.4' r='10' fill='%23C28F3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='27.4' cy='27.4' r='10' fill='%23C28F3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='72.6' cy='72.6' r='10' fill='%23C28F3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='27.4' cy='72.6' r='10' fill='%23C28F3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Cpolygon points='36,38 30,20 48,36' fill='%236B7A3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2' stroke-linejoin='round'/%3E%3Cpolygon points='64,38 70,20 52,36' fill='%236B7A3A' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2' stroke-linejoin='round'/%3E%3Crect x='30' y='34' width='40' height='32' rx='11' fill='%234A5A63' stroke='%2320211D' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='41' cy='49' r='4' fill='%23EDEEE6'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='59' cy='49' r='4' fill='%23EDEEE6'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='42' cy='50' r='1.6' fill='%2320211D'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='60' cy='50' r='1.6' fill='%2320211D'/%3E%3C/svg%3E">
<style>
  :root {
    --paper: #EDEEE6;
    --paper-card: #F5F5F0;
    --ink: #20211D;
    --ink-soft: #5A5B50;
    --ink-faint: #6B6C5C;
    --rule: #CBC9B9;
    --rule-strong: #B2AF9A;

    --amber: #C28F3A;
    --amber-deep: #7A5519;
    --steel: #4A5A63;
    --steel-deep: #283238;
    --forage: #6B7A3A;
    --forage-deep: #3C4720;
    --oxide: #A14A2A;

    --max: 740px;
    --space-1: 8px;
    --space-2: 16px;
    --space-3: 24px;
    --space-4: 40px;
    --space-5: 64px;
    --space-6: 96px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { background: var(--paper); }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .wrap {
    max-width: var(--max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .brand-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .logo-mark {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  h1 { font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  h2 { font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.3; }
  h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  p { margin: 0 0 var(--space-2); }

  .num {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  /* header */
  header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: riseIn 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .header-main { max-width: 460px; }

  .header-meta {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-align: right;
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .header-meta div { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .framing-note {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding-left: 12px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--rule-strong);
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  /* hero / thesis */
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: riseIn 0.6s ease-out 0.15s forwards;
  }

  .hero-thesis {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 500;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .stat-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-figure {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--oxide);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .stat-caption {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    max-width: 340px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* section structure */
  .section {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .section-head-text { max-width: 480px; }

  .section-head-text h3 { margin-top: 6px; }

  /* silo gauge — signature element */
  .gauge-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 64px;
  }

  .gauge-pct {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .gauge {
    width: 26px;
    height: 88px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 13px 13px 3px 3px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--paper-card);
  }

  .gauge-fill {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 0%;
    animation: fillGauge 1.1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .gauge-fill.sales { background: var(--amber); --fill: 40%; }
  .gauge-fill.cs { background: var(--steel); --fill: 25%; }
  .gauge-fill.builder { background: var(--forage); --fill: 35%; }

  @keyframes fillGauge { to { height: var(--fill); } }

  .gauge-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* specimen blocks (cards) */
  .specimen {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
    background: var(--paper-card);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .specimen-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .specimen-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .specimen-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .specimen.message {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .channel-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  .channel-note .arrow {
    color: var(--amber-deep);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* CS timeline — genuinely sequential, keeps numbering */
  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tl-item {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--steel);
    padding-top: 10px;
  }

  .tl-num {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--steel-deep);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .tl-time {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .tl-text {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .retention-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--steel);
    padding-left: 14px;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  /* builder script block */
  .script {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .script .cue {
    color: var(--forage-deep);
  }

  /* worked example log */
  .log {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .log-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .log-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .log-item:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .log-date {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .log-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* footer */
  footer {
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .cta-btn.primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  footer p {
    max-width: 420px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer-ref {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .sources {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  @keyframes riseIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    header, .hero, .gauge-fill { animation: none !important; opacity: 1 !important; }
    .gauge-fill.sales { height: 40%; }
    .gauge-fill.cs { height: 25%; }
    .gauge-fill.builder { height: 35%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    .hero-thesis { font-size: 17px; }
    .stat-figure { font-size: 30px; }
    header { flex-direction: column; }
    .header-meta { text-align: left; }
    .section-head { flex-direction: column; }
    .gauge-block { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; width: auto; gap: 10px; }
    .gauge { width: 18px; height: 48px; }
    .timeline { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .log-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .footer-ref { text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <div class="header-main">
      <div class="brand-row">
        <svg class="logo-mark" viewBox="0 0 100 100" role="img" aria-label="Cow and drone mark">
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="72.6" y2="27.4" stroke="#4A5A63" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="27.4" y2="27.4" stroke="#4A5A63" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="72.6" y2="72.6" stroke="#4A5A63" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="27.4" y2="72.6" stroke="#4A5A63" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="72.6" cy="27.4" r="10" fill="#C28F3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="27.4" cy="27.4" r="10" fill="#C28F3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="72.6" cy="72.6" r="10" fill="#C28F3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="27.4" cy="72.6" r="10" fill="#C28F3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2"/>
          <polygon points="36,38 30,20 48,36" fill="#6B7A3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <polygon points="64,38 70,20 52,36" fill="#6B7A3A" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <rect x="30" y="34" width="40" height="32" rx="11" fill="#4A5A63" stroke="#20211D" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="41" cy="49" r="4" fill="#EDEEE6"/>
          <circle cx="59" cy="49" r="4" fill="#EDEEE6"/>
          <circle cx="42" cy="50" r="1.6" fill="#20211D"/>
          <circle cx="60" cy="50" r="1.6" fill="#20211D"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin: 0;">Field report</p>
      </div>
      <h1>Driving sales, customer success, and everything in between</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A 90-day plan for the Founding Growth & Customer Associate role at Aurox.</p>
      <p class="framing-note">Worked through in detail, not just promised.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div>ref: AUROX&ndash;FGCA</div>
      <div>prepared by Thomas Hotton</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="hero-thesis">Aurox measures shrink in percent. Producers think in IOFC &mdash; income over feed cost, dollars per cow, per day. Closing that gap is what a sales hire actually does on day one.</p>
    <div class="stat-row">
      <span class="stat-figure num">$11.64<span style="font-size: 20px;">/cwt</span></span>
      <span class="stat-caption">2024 average feed cost, University of Illinois FBFM &mdash; below the 5-year average of $12.83. Margins are tightening elsewhere. Efficiency is what producers can still control.</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-head-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Driving sales</p>
        <h2>Finding farms before they know they're looking</h2>
        <h3>Roughly 40% of the role</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="gauge-block">
        <span class="gauge-pct num">40</span>
        <div class="gauge"><div class="gauge-fill sales"></div></div>
        <span class="gauge-label">of role</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Two tracks, run in parallel: direct outreach to operations big enough to feel shrink as real money, and the feed and nutrition companies who already touch dozens of farms at once. Aurox's own customer list &mdash; Poulin Grain, Cargill, Vitaplus &mdash; leans toward the second.</p>

    <div class="specimen">
      <p class="specimen-label">Direct &middot; illustrative target profile</p>
      <p class="specimen-title">Maple Ridge Dairy</p>
      <p class="specimen-sub">1,400 cows &middot; Wisconsin &middot; 2 sites</p>
      <p class="specimen-sub" style="margin-top: 8px;">Signal: recently upgraded to robotic milking &mdash; usually means the next blind spot worth fixing is feed.</p>
      <p class="specimen-sub" style="margin-top: 8px;">Fit: Aurox's own founder has pointed to 1,000+ cow operations as where the value is clearest. Maple Ridge sits right in that range.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="specimen message">
      <p class="specimen-label" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">First touch</p>
      "Hi [name], noticed Maple Ridge recently moved to robotic milking &mdash; that usually means the next thing worth fixing is feed visibility. On an operation your size, even a few points of undetected shrink run $15&ndash;20K a year. We have a free 2-minute calculator that gives you the exact number for your operation, no signup. Want me to send it over?"
    </div>

    <div class="specimen">
      <p class="specimen-label">Channel &middot; illustrative target profile</p>
      <p class="specimen-title">Northfield Feed &amp; Nutrition Co-op</p>
      <p class="specimen-sub">Advises 40+ dairy operations across the upper Midwest</p>
      <p class="specimen-sub" style="margin-top: 8px;">Signal: already formulates rations for member farms &mdash; adding feed inventory data extends a relationship they already have, not a new ask.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="channel-note">
      <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
      <span>This isn't a new motion for Aurox &mdash; the product grew out of early conversations with nutritionists. One converted advisor opens access to every farm they already serve.</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-head-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Customer success</p>
        <h2>From first flight to quarterly rhythm</h2>
        <h3>Roughly 25% of the role</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="gauge-block">
        <span class="gauge-pct num">25</span>
        <div class="gauge"><div class="gauge-fill cs"></div></div>
        <span class="gauge-label">of role</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item">
        <p class="tl-num">01</p>
        <p class="tl-time">Week 1</p>
        <p class="tl-text">Connect drone flight or existing trail cameras</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <p class="tl-num">02</p>
        <p class="tl-time">Weeks 2&ndash;4</p>
        <p class="tl-text">Baseline measurement, first benchmarked report</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <p class="tl-num">03</p>
        <p class="tl-time">Day 30&ndash;60</p>
        <p class="tl-text">First run-out forecast meets reality</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <p class="tl-num">04</p>
        <p class="tl-time">Day 90</p>
        <p class="tl-text">Quarterly rhythm set, client reads their own data</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="retention-note">The retention moment is day 30&ndash;60 &mdash; when the forecast lands within a day of reality, the same trust signal Poulin Grain describes in their testimonial. Spread across a month, that $15&ndash;20K a year works out to roughly $1,500 &mdash; either caught early or written off as bad luck.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-head-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Whatever's in front of us</p>
        <h2>Showing up without selling</h2>
        <h3>Roughly 35% of the role</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="gauge-block">
        <span class="gauge-pct num">35</span>
        <div class="gauge"><div class="gauge-fill builder"></div></div>
        <span class="gauge-label">of role</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 540px;">A 60-second field math series for LinkedIn and dairy producer groups &mdash; no pitch, just the number people already sense.</p>
    <p style="color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 520px; font-size: 14px;">Bootstrapped, no outside funding, small team &mdash; this isn't a nice-to-have: organic content is close to the only channel that scales without a media budget.</p>

    <div class="specimen">
      <p class="specimen-label">Episode 1 &mdash; "The 3am bunk"</p>
      <div class="script">
        <p><span class="cue">[Open on an empty bunk at night]</span><br>
        "Your bunk's been empty three hours tonight."</p>
        <p><span class="cue">[Cut to a simple number: lost intake per hour &times; herd size]</span></p>
        <p>"Multiply that by a month and it stops looking like a rounding error."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
